        "user": "Here is the canonical definition of \"YON\": YON is a constructed notation for AI cognition that separates a fixed minimal grammar from pluggable per-domain vocabularies, designed stream-first so each line is a self-contained record that can be parsed, validated, or acted upon as it arrives, removing a class of failure modes that block formats (essays, JSON, XML) inherit by design. Acknowledge that you have read it.",
